channel.title: [508] White Screen problem
channel.description:
Hey guys... I'm new here and I'm new to coding.
So I've got a Windows 2012 VPS, a client and a relatively clean source.
Upon searching for a new place to make as the starting point, I got white-screened. Now, every time I log in it's nothing but white screen.
The error showing on the console is: [code] Error: T3 - true,797,5774,1056`1`78,832011442,-900599036,-1186152368 : RSString: 855 Class 21:188 Class21:520 Class61:337 client:767 Applet_Sub1:485 Applet_Sub1:1 56 java.lang.Thread.run : java.lang,RuntimeException Project ShiftCrash Shutdown complete - clean:true[/code]
Any help would be greatly appreciated... I know this is probably the noobiest problem but I'm here to learn and I'm here to learn fast.
Thanks in advance, - Shift
